{"tid":1119864,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"搞野真係好重要","createTime":"2019-04-22T08:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T09:33:52.000Z","uid":1369,"like":11,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"73eddedd2b6c5849d418cb01d4bb80170fe419df","tid":1119864,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的 最初同女友搞野果時真係會射濕成張床<br />\n直至拍拖第4個年頭 依家同女友搞野已經愈來愈唔識硬 仲好軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n硬係覺得佢同我扑只為咗自己 我覺得自己好似鴨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似所有女人都係為叫而叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾終於分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過咗半年 有個gay佬不停追我 但我地無一齊 <br />\n有次飲完酒 gay佬搞我 我射到好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />第一次同男人搞野 我好緊張 不安&hellip;<br />\n但唔明點解可以覺得舒服過以往同女人搞野咁 到底我係直定gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家我地關係好似sp咁&hellip;到底我應該揀返個女人拍拖 定 試下同gay佬一齊？<br />\n<br />\n利申 17歲 以往拍拖對像都係女性"},{"pid":"a02b7f0dce57c5f1e754b4181822bb9da0bd7492","tid":1119864,"uid":186844,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:53:36.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"09f7c7494a8c2f5d03f4ead6c07aba16d36ef03d","tid":1119864,"uid":17426,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:53:47.000Z","msg":"試下3p比較下"},{"pid":"f414b851f5b2d8a239438847a82fcc12b7367251","tid":1119864,"uid":175645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T08:59:16.000Z","msg":"睇到係連登名人都知你唔係17歲"},{"pid":"9f3ab31b9d15796763f1555fcea9cc019b1dce71","tid":1119864,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"若果你真係17歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> &hellip;&hellip;&hellip